Description_lang: Ysera's Gift now heals every ${$s2/1000} sec and its healing is increased by $s1% for each of your active Rejuvenations.

description_blz.en_US: Ysera's Gift now heals every 4 sec and its healing is increased by 8% for each of your active Rejuvenations.

description_blz.de_DE: 'Yseras Gabe' heilt jetzt alle 4 Sek. und jeder Eurer aktiven Effekte von 'Verjüngung' erhöht die Heilung um 8%.

description_blz.ko_KR: 이제 이세라의 선물이 4초마다 치유하고 회복이 활성화된 대상 하나당 치유량이 8%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 伊瑟拉的贈禮現在每4秒會恢復生命力，你每一個作用中的回春術會使伊瑟拉的贈禮的治療量提高8%。
